headline: Fifth Third Again Named Best Treasury and Cash Management Bank by Global Finance
summary: CINCINNATI, July 22, 2025--Fifth Third (NASDAQ: FITB) was again named Best Treasury and Cash Management Bank (US, Regional) by Global Finance magazine for 2025. This makes Fifth Third a two-time honoree in the Midwest region, and this year, Fifth Third was also recognized in the Southeast region. The award was announced by Global Finance as part of its 25th annual Best Treasury and Cash Management Banks Award program.
